title: 11 new songs your favourite musicians have released in the last 11 days : Music, News - India Today
text:
Music 11 new songs your favourite musicians have released in the last 11 days Coldplay, Ed Sheeran, Lana Del Ray, Selena Gomez..Phew! Nearly all your favourite musicians have come out with new songs. IndiaToday.in | Posted by Mini Dixit A + A - 
Merely two months into 2017 and some of world's most favourite musicians have already treated our senses to some brilliant music. While the addiction quotient of each song is debatable, the quantity is overwhelming to say the least. 
With Coldplay and The Chainsmokers' latest track, Something Just Like This, being the latest addition to the list of new songs bestowed upon us in the last two weeks, we being to you a list of out top 11 picks. 
Also Read: Ed Sheeran reveals why Taylor Swift 's music never gets leaked 
From Selena Gomez's EDM-ish track It Ain't Me to Linkin Park's comeback track, Heavy, this list deserves your attention and it deserves it now.
